column2: "Fwuahahaha hahaha! This is good. So you were led here, too, eh?"
"You don't know what I mean? Don't play dumb! You feel the dark vibe in this place, too, right?"
"Did Zeno tell you not to talk to me?"
"A respectable ARKS member like you has no reason to talk to someone like me!"
"Hmm? Where's Sheena? Do you want her?"
"Too bad! I'm not handing her over. Someone that useful is hard to come by."
"But look at this! Is there anything more beautiful than this? Sends chills down my spine."
"Fwuhahahaha! Hey, hey! Do you know how long I've been waiting for this?"
"Catch my drift? Now stop loitering and get lost!"
"Go home and cry like the pantywaist you are! That suits you better than being here."
